cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI 

This paper discusses cooperative training methods for distributed machine learning with wireless communication links, which involves topics related to machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), control systems (cs.SY), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). However, since the focus is on machine learning and wireless communication, cs.LG and cs.IT are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes and evaluates digital and over-the-air computing implementations, which further supports the inclusion of cs.IT and cs.NI. Finally, the use of heterogeneous data suggests a potential connection to cs.AI.
